{
  "texts": [
    "The robot then takes the most optimal action w.r.t.",
    "to the simulated game.",
    "We formalize this idea with Algorithm 1.Let us assume that a model M of the training environment is provided.",
    "It can be a distribution or sample model learned during training.",
    "It also can be a simulation engine if the agent is trained in a virtual world."
  ]
}